One source, the report stated, "explained that Moscow's business owners understand that it is best to get the protection of the MVD and SFS (rather than organized crime groups) since they not only have more weapons, resources and power than criminal groups, but are also protected by law."
"For this reason, protection against criminal gangs is no longer a priority."
