He pointed out that "the minimum" would be for the PQ to apologize.
The consortia formula is a common practice throughout the world.
Typically, it is an alliance with a time limit that allows two or several companies to pool their knowledge to respond to a tender for a complex project.
The Eastmain project presents a high level of complexity, considering the magnitude of the works.
The works have already begun and will last until 2012.
