A quick look at Quebec's commercial register identifies more than 200 consortia, some of which appear permanent.
In this way, Dessau works in partnership with most of its main competitors, such as CIMA+, Génivar, SNC-Lavalin, Roche et Tecsult, and others.
Each combination, and there are dozens of them, leads to a single legal entity, namely Dessau.
